 website wwwrmgnetworkscom current status active rmg networks formerly symon communications is a digital signage company headquartered in texas it provides digital signage media hardware software and services to nearly  of the fortune  rmg networks provides data visualization for a variety of application areas including contact centers supply chain operations and internal communication to leading industries including financial services healthcare hospitality higher education government manufacturing retail telecommunications transportation and utilities rmg is headquartered in dallas with offices in the united states united kingdom singapore and the united arab emirates the companys stock is traded on nasdaq under the ticker symbol rmgn historyedit reach media group was founded in  as danoo and got financial backing from kleiner perkins caufield  byers dag ventures national cinemedia and tennenbaum capital partners in july  danoo acquired ideacast in august  the company renamed itself rmg networks and appointed garry mcguire to take over as ceo from aileen lee in may  rmg sold its digital signage network targeting cafes small restaurants and juice bars for an undisclosed sum to san franciscobased brite media in april  the company acquired symon communications a digital signage company founded in  for  million and moved its headquarters from san francisco to the dallas metropolitan area where symon communications was located the company went public via a reverse merger with scg financial acquisition corp in april  external linksedit rmg networks rmg networks investor relations referencesedit  httpwwwrmgnetworkscomnewsrmgnetworksnamesrobertmichelsonceo  danoo acquires ideacast to put ads in gyms and airplanes venturebeat july    danoo  ideacast relaunch as reach media group dailydooh august    danoo lands new chief executive for digital outofhome ads venturebeat july    rmg acquires symon communications mediapost april    digital signage biz rmg networks goes public a